User Story: As a homebuyer, I want to be to search for brokers

Given that I am on the homebuyer’s homepage. 
When I enter the name of the broker in the search bar.
Then the system should display the specified broker. 

Given that I am on the homebuyer’s homepage.
When I enter the name of the broker that doesn’t exist in the search bar. 
Then the system should display an error message indicating that this broker doesn’t exist.

